{"tid":1450140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚傷亡慘重 但一定要記住","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:52:20.000Z","uid":13189,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e2d0e0e756c473765f0a6faedea35d1c5d6a25e4","tid":1450140,"uid":13189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:21:24.000Z","msg":"過左今晚 一定要瘋狂煲大<br />\n1. 警黑合作 放任黑社會/大陸幫周街打人<br />\n2. 黑警平射子彈 奪去女義士既視力<br />\n3. 係地鐵站射催淚彈 唔跟指引使用 罔顧市民安全<br />\n4. 近距離對示威者連續開槍<br />\n5. 無示威活動下 係屋苑射催淚彈<br />\n6. 黑警喬裝扮成示威者 煽動暴力行為<br />\n7. 香港政府無視現況 不回應 五大訴求 不管束 警隊濫暴行為<br />\n<br />\n我知一定唔只依7樣，請自行加上去<br />\n<br />\n一定要靠文宣 傳媒 國際輿論去煲大佢。去到依一刻警黑 濫暴已經好明顯，啲狗搞足18區咁濟，只要再加大量文宣已經可以攞到<br />\n大量民意。請大家好好利用依啲證據<br />\n<br />\n百萬人塞爆機場係好，但諗諗 搞得咁倉卒，唔夠宣傳到時又係無人。我覺得最好就係聽日即刻開多次記者會，再呼籲大家響應會好過聽日即刻搞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命 真。雙普選"},{"pid":"bf541f08bf4bf7ddff3449853c54b2063185b66e","tid":1450140,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:22:45.000Z","msg":"死黑警死全家"},{"pid":"e4da1df4fabb924b24eaec5a674624935c234c91","tid":1450140,"uid":73565,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:22:47.000Z","msg":"煲大左又點<br />\n香港人致命傷就係成日以為會有人打救<br />\n連自己都唔救自己"},{"pid":"2a936027ef29f7580a721bd3a9dd856987b6aa8b","tid":1450140,"uid":78033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:23:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3316d1282e43918003b7519b3513d395e96f3226","tid":1450140,"uid":163024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:24:12.000Z","msg":"凌晨荃灣綠楊天橋下面白衫無差別攻擊，突然叫曬救命無任何警察"},{"pid":"a9aeed3fefd4a16ae4e50a6b9636ea31ad8052bc","tid":1450140,"uid":13189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:26:12.000Z","msg":"721721721<br />\n811811811"},{"pid":"a7a0ac3853db11cafb797c3139257c514768d635","tid":1450140,"uid":13189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:26:23.000Z","msg":"721721721<br />\n811811811"},{"pid":"d440353126167ab2acf0b9900b6ee552dbd3232e","tid":1450140,"uid":78033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:29:04.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 非公職時參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証<br />\n6.太古地鐵站零距離開槍<br />\n7.荃灣綠楊 白衫人接力 無差別攻擊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8329feb4f23906bdd8f0759066195896c7528074","tid":1450140,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:29:20.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"a1f550bb877a55db442cdd443994434603e28387","tid":1450140,"uid":78033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:30:33.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9392e788488e943c4abe2f54dc2d1fec0cf2ed84","tid":1450140,"uid":13189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:33:24.000Z","msg":"721811721811<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095109348f91b819f1665af53b1d924aa6d3f847","tid":1450140,"uid":254450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:36:36.000Z","msg":"翻版64"},{"pid":"ffc7857f99a112aeb345261f080010386b7a9158","tid":1450140,"uid":144084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:37:08.000Z","msg":"狗舍位置合集<br />\n主動攻勢，咪再比狗帶到有利佢地既地方開戰！<br />\n禍必及妻兒 ! 攻敵所必救！<br />\n唔好做犯法野，小心D~~<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441328